{
  "stem": "25651.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we sent it to Switzerland to an uncle-- incidentally, that was one other thing, that we were going to join Father through this address in Switzerland, which was a man called Avraham [?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Heizelbach, ?] who was the brother of my uncle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother's sister, Perla, married Zev [INAUDIBLE], who was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Heizelbach. ?] They lived in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have cousins called [INAUDIBLE] now in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the whole story about Perla and how she died and how it influenced my mother to be anti-Zionist, and my mother's attitude to the war, it's all tied up with the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't go into it, because it's too-- it's a book.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's my mother's tragedy, which is a completely different story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was talking about us being in the transport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were already on the ramp boarding the train, when, again, Leo appears with a-- with a wheelbarrow this time and a stretcher party.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he's got a paper which says that this family has a contagious disease.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He doesn't say it's my family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, this family has a contagious disease.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have to take them-- I have here an order to take them straight to quarantine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they stay, the whole train will arrive dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What a prospect.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And Leo had that sort of-- he spoke German perfectly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he was allowed to take these three people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And off we went, back into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You probably don't know, but when the transports were being got ready, each train was 2,500 people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when the Germans said 2,500, they meant 2,500.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If people died-- there was a barracks where everybody, 2,500 people, waited until the train came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The train came now all ready.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The railway station was outside this barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
